@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded shadow-sm">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center fw-bold">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p class="text-muted text-center">Effective Date: June 18, 2025</p>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">1. Introduction</h4>
            <p>This website is a personal portfolio created and maintained by <strong>Mohammed Marjan Ahmed Mashud</strong> to showcase skills, projects, and experience. Your privacy is important, and this policy outlines how your information is collected, used, and protected.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">2. Information Collected</h4>
            <p>This site only collects personal information when voluntarily submitted through the contact form. This may include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Phone number (optional)</li>
                <li>Message content</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">3. Use of Information</h4>
            <p>Any information provided is used solely to respond to inquiries. It is never sold, shared, or used for unsolicited contact.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">4. Email Communication</h4>
            <p>Messages submitted via the contact form are delivered via secure SMTP directly to the my email. No data is stored on the website's server.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">5. Cookies & Analytics</h4>
            <p>This site may use cookies or basic analytics tools to enhance the user experience. No personal data is tracked or used for advertising purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">6. Data Security</h4>
            <p>Reasonable precautions are taken to secure any personal data you submit. However, no internet transmission is completely secure.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">7. Third-Party Links</h4>
            <p>Links to external websites (e.g. LinkedIn, Itch.io) are not governed by this policy. Please review their individual privacy policies.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">8. Changes to This Policy</h4>
            <p>This policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will definitely be reflected here with an updated date.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold">9. Contact</h4>
            <p>If you have questions or concerns about this policy, please email <a href="mailto:marjan14362@gmail.com">marjan14362@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    h1, h4 {
        color: #333;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 900px;
    }
</style>
